column1: Regular traffic reports will resume Thursday August 13 at 6:30 a.m.

column3: TRAFFIC ALERT for I-75 at 117 MM (the northern 75/64 split)
column4: No access to I-75N toward Georgetown from the northern 75/64 split due to collision investigation in Scott Co.  I-75N is shutdown near the 125 MM in Scott Co until further notice.

column3: TRAFFIC ALERT for I-75 at 117 MM (the northern 75/64 split)
column4: All traffic on I-75N is being diverted to I-64W, and traffic on I-64E must continue on I-75S toward Newtown Pike.
